<div style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 20px 24px; background: #F7F7F7; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; color: #515151; max-width: 1290px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0;"><strong style="color: #222222;">Testing methodology:</strong> TTFB measured from 22 US locations • Load test: 0-100 concurrent users • &#x26a0; indicates 4xx/5xx errors during load testing • Rankings based on overall performance score (TTFB 40%, Uptime 40%, Load handling 20%) + unique selling proposition (USP)</p>
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong style="color: #222222;">Real-World Performance Testing:</strong> Identical WordPress sites deployed across all hosting providers • Benchmarking Tools: Pingdom synthetic monitoring and Loader.io • Test Site Setup: Twenty Twenty-Four theme, standardized plugins (Akismet, Contact Form 7 and Rank Math) • Key Metrics Measured: TTFB (speed), uptime and load handling response time.</p>
</div>
